		<exercise xml:id="ckpt_conditional_bayes-1">
			<statement>
				<p>The following tree diagram depicts the outcomes in a two-step experiment. Use it to answer the question below.</p>
				<figure xml:id="fig_conditional_ckpt_bayes-1">
					<caption></caption>
